msgstr "A vision of heaven's gates"

msgid "NARRATIVE_JACOBS_LADDER_MAIN"
msgstr "Jacob dreamed of a ladder reaching to heaven,\nwith angels ascending and descending.\n\nGod renewed His promise there."

